---
import '../styles/collaboration.scss';
---
<section class="collaboration">
    <div class="collaboration-content">
        <div class="collaboration-content-box title">
            <h2>Our Collaboration</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="collaboration-content-box web">
            <h2>Web Development</h2>
            <p>Transform your business with dynamic, responsive websites tailored to your needs. Let’s create a stunning digital presence that drives engagement and growth.</p>
            <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack">
                <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack-item"><img src="/images/apps/webflow.svg" alt="Webflow"></div>
                <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack-item"><img src="/images/apps/framer.svg" alt="Framer"></div>
                <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack-item"><img src="/images/apps/squarespace.svg" alt="Squarespace"></div>
                <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack-item"><img src="/images/apps/wordpress.svg" alt="Wordpress"></div>
                <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack-item"><img src="/images/apps/custom.svg" alt="Custom code"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="collaboration-content-box uiux">
            <h2>UI/UX</h2>
            <p>Elevate your brand with user-centric designs that are both beautiful and functional. I craft layouts that ensure seamless user flow and memorable experiences.</p>
            <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack">
                <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack-item"><img src="/images/apps/figma.svg" alt="Figma"></div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="collaboration-content-box branding">
            <h2>Branding</h2>
            <p>Let’s enhance your business brand with consistent style guides, hierarchy, and imagery that convey your essence and mission to users.</p>
            <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack">
                <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack-item"><img src="/images/apps/figma.svg" alt="Figma"></div>
                <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack-item"><img src="/images/apps/ai.svg" alt="Ai"></div>
                <div class="collaboration-content-box-stack-item"><img src="/images/apps/ps.svg" alt="Ps"></div>
            </div>

        </div>

       
    </div>